Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:05.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:08.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.70,0:00:09.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:13.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:16.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who waits upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:20.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is a formal guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.17,0:00:22.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who is there to support his mistress \Nin all aspects of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:24.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:29.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This is about a boy who fights \Nand puts his life on the line or a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:32.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A super combat battle story!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Hayate. Earth is being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is also being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:45.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi ni kaketa bokura no yukue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:45.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination that we've \Nstaked upon this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuki-nukeru hayate no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sudden gale that cuts across
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:55.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Unmei ni makete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:55.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to fate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:00.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shagami-komu nante tsumannai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:00.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And hunkering down is no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:04.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore ja kakko warui yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:04.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso kara deta makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Many a true word is spoken in jest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:13.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koukai wa kitto mi kara deta sabi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:13.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret is probably reaping what you sowed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:16.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zettai, nase ba naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:16.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a will, \Nthere's definitely a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:23.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ooki na hamon ni nomi-komareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:23.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As a great rippling wave swallows us up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:29.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Karada nami ni makasereba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:29.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it take you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:32.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanchigai no yume
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:32.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams that are misguided
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:36.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mato-hazure no kitai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:36.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes that are way off base
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:41.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyoku omoeba itsuka tsukameru sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:41.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grab them someday, \Nif you just have conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:48.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi keri-age hashiri-dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:48.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick up the earth and start running
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:55.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimama ni mau kaze no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:55.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:11.48,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You Say You Can See Time, But That Is \NProbably Your Life Flashing Before Your Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's you, Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got here quicker than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried that you might \Nhave gotten lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry for worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everything is fine, \Nbecause I {\i1}did{\i0} get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone I believe to be your new \Nbutler brought me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You met Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was wearing a brand new cashmere coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that definitely sounds \Nlike it was Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he may end up dying if we don't hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Hayate in some kind of trouble again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's certainly conceivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good! Hayate's in a fix! \NWe're going to save him, Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it was a bad idea to make him \Nwear something he wasn't used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That cashmere coat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:06.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It is certainly the first crisis he has faced \Nsince he became a butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, Maria! We must hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:26.97,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(144,58.5)}Cash Advance!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't do something about this coat,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never be able to go back \Nto the estate again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:22.12,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should just borrow money \Nfrom somewhere and get a new coat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:24.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't solve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ayasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You people are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "very generous people", \Nwho previously kindly offered
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to send me to a tropical paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about embarrassing things \Nin an expository manner on the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck, you're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But well, if it weren't \Nfor our business dealings,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I could've liked a guy like ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even our chance meetin' \Nmust've been fated somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If ya want, I'll treat ya to a meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ayasaki, who're these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to even ask. They've gotta be Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Colleagues of ours, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were suspicious \Nfrom the start, but so you really are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, four-eyes, you got \Na problem with our boy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! When did I become one of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you seem to be determined \Nto see some bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you guys are, \Nbut you've got guts, I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:37.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become involved in a pretty \Nnasty situation, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, never mind \Nbeing reprimanded by Maria,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:41.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get chewed out \Nby the authorities and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:45.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Above all, this may cause problems \Nfor the Miss and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:47.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to escape somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where do you think \Nyou're going, Ayasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not planning on deserting \Nyour comrades, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said earlier, when \Ndid I become one of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Trying to save his own hide \Nby deserting his comrades?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coldhearted bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I'm getting condemned \Nby the other side, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I guess we've got no choice \Nbut to whack him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:17.12,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to die today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:21.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, today's just been an awful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If this was how it was going to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:27.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I'd offered a sincere apology \Nto Maria back at the estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:38.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if I make it back alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:40.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll offer a sincere apology \Nfor sure this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you dragging your \Nfeet for?! We must hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing Hayate, if we drag our feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he may be skewered by countless \Nswords before we know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, nothing so drastic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, the new coat may be in tatters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can bet on it! \NDon't underestimate Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the coat is already in tatters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's Hayate for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The coat had gotten dirty because of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was very troubled by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shows just how serious he is \Nabout his job as Nagi's butler...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you put it that way, we can't be \Ntoo hard on him for ruining the coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't going to be hard on him \Nfor it to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he seems to have \Ncome home at the perfect time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a hopeless guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank goodness. \NI managed to get back alive somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, you are not to scold Hayate, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must give him a warm welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you say so, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, \Ndid Hayate say anything about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, anything \Nabout me being cute or charming...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, as I recall, he said you were \Na little, spoiled, headstrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and an unmanageable bundle of energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?! Why did you shut the door?! Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Stupid jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But also kind and adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would work better \Nif you mentioned that earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:40.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,all too soon, the butler-in-debt's \Nmiserable life came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please, no jokes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:48.61,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Fox Udon Dontaro
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry, it seems I am making \Nsuch trouble for everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,38.9 degrees. He's unmistakably \Ncome down with a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather may have suddenly \Ngotten cooler, but to catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How weak can you be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know anything \Nabout him being weak, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When {\i1}someone{\i0} locked him out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to spend hours in soaking wet \Nclothes in this cold weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's no wonder that he caught a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound as though I'm the bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in pain, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me with eyes like Kenshiro's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like when he mastered the Musou Tensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an unavoidable accident \Nthat you caught a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just relax and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this is a milkshake. \NIt will warm you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While the fact that Nagi \Nshut you out was the final blow,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the original cause lies with me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:21.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This was Isumi trying to cover \Nfor Nagi in her own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is true that the Miss \Ndelivered the final blow, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea that you went \Nto the same school as the Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am the one who leapt \Nto the horribly wrong conclusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, please do not let that bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'll enjoy this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Though, I do not know \Nif it will be to your taste...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so glad it is to your taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made this yourself, right? \NI see that you must be a good cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know if I am good or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I {\i1}am{\i0} a girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wrong to think that you should cook, \Njust because you're a girl, Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With such antiquated notions,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you won't survive \Nin the information age to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, you only use big words when \Nyou are trying to cover up something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know her so very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, men and women are equal \Nin the 21st century! No boundaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having said that, you still haven't \Neven had lunch, right, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I shall put special effort into \Nmaking some dish called "rice porridge".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with that? \NYou didn't sound very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or what? Are you saying you \Ndon't want to eat my cooking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, my heart is bursting with gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then prepare \Nyourself and wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have read through every volume of \N"Mister Ajikko" and "Gourmand-kun".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no dish that I cannot make!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Meow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with your weak response, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall go prepare \Nsome stomach medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hang in there, my dear Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:10.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus, Miss Nagi's \Nministrations began. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:14.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No, considering how \Nconfident the Miss seems,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,surely her dish won't be that terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:20.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate could find no way to convince \Nhimself that he would recover soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, Saku? \NI didn't know you were still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got sucked into the Downtown DVD \Nbox set, but then I got hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I am about to begin cooking,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll let you have a taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops! I've still got DVDs \Nthat I gotta watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since I'm going to \Nthe trouble of making this,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try seasoning it in a \Nunique and distinctive way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:48.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first mistake \Nthat amateur cooks fall for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I want some punchy flavor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, vinegar's supposed to be good for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:55.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If yer forced to eat Nagi's cookin',
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,it won't be enough, no matter \Nhow many lives you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:03.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate might end up dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sakuya, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm so sorry about this, Isumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, because Hayate has \Ncaused you all kinds of trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, it was no trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can see why my Nagi \Nput her trust in him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was quite kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:30.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this possibly mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:34.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...that once again, Hayate \Nis spreading a kind of ailment
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:36.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,that's even more troublesome than a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Master! ({\i1}I{\i0}rasshaimase goshujin-sa{\i1}ma{\i0})
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now. ({\i1}M{\i0}aa, maa, ma{\i1}a{\i0})
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, it's ready, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite confident of how it turned out, \Nso eat it with that in mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? This looks better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:54.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just possible...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, then I shall enjoy it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind the poor use of salt
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:06.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,or that it subtly tastes like sushi rice \Nor that it's not fully cooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Before all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:10.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell the faint aroma of \Nthe detergent used in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:14.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This can no longer even be called food...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, could it be that it didn't taste good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:21.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that there are times
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:25.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,when a man's pride requires \Nthat he see something through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is very... delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:29.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids, you must never try this at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:32.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because detergent \Nis neither food nor drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see! I'm glad to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't tasted it, so I was worried, \Nbut I guess it turned out good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's absolutely fantastic, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bit of oil I used for subtle \Nflavor must have worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty more, \Nso go ahead and eat it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's so good! Oh! My Konbu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a glutton, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:59.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To live up to the mistress's expectations! \NThat is what a butler does!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.56,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}OIL comes off easily! \NMarmar Lemon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:04.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that she used this, \Nmistaking it for oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:09.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To live up to the mistress's expectations! \NThat is what a pet does!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Meow... Meow... Meow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you for the food...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you really cleaned your plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been awfully hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll go clean this up, \Nso get some good sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yessir...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:26.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunate things \Nare always happening to me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:29.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Today was kind of amazingly \Nworse than usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you push yourself too hard, \Nyou really will end up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! I'm amazed \Nthat you managed to eat all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, I mean, she put in detergent \Ninstead of oil by mistake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Miss worked hard to make \Nthat dish for me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, it made me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I had someone taking \Ncare me while I was sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your mother not take care \Nof you when you got sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether her child got a fever \Nor was severely injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my mother was the sort \Nwho blithely ignored it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and just invested in her dreams \Nwhere the reels keep spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:11.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}Sign: Lunch Money
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.80,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sign: Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:19.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this boy! Casually mentioning \Nsuch a depressing story...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at any rate, please \Nget some rest for today, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will, I'm so sleepy already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, what are you doing, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is... With your face so close to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's hard for me to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Hayate, you stupid jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:16.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that good people die young, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:19.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I sort of understand why now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:25.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus, the poverty-stricken \Nbutler's hellish day came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:33.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A good night's sleep \Nand I'm completely over my cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:37.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to do anything yesterday, \Nso I better work hard today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... right... Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather is so fine today, \Nit's perfect for laundry, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, you are a Sanzenin butler, \Nand yet your strong tie is crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should pay close attention \Nto your personal appearance,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so as not to be an embarrassment \Nto your mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, good day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is someone strange in the residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she's wearing a maid outfit \Nthat's different from yours
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she wears glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Any other \Ndistinguishing characteristics?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to say, she looks \Nincredibly capable,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's unmistakably a natural born klutz!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is not a problem, so please go \Nabout your morning cleaning duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, also, I believe we should \Nhave one other visitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so when you see that person, \Nplease show them to the drawing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone from the Tachibana family is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:18:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it appears Saki is here, \Nso security must have let them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have some suspicious \Nindividuals inside the residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive them out immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I don't care how you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.89,0:18:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even permit \Nthe non-lethal use of firearms!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get rid of them right away! That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to actually kick them out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I don't want Hayate to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:30.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,She said we should have another visitor...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man, I wish the Earth \Nwould just get destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:40.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is with this boy, \Nmuttering such disturbing things...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.46,0:18:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk so familiarly to me \Nwith your poor-looking face, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:50.12,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:51.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:56.36,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this most impudent child \Nis the guest Maria was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear! I'm in the crappiest mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just bored, so would you go jump \Ninto that pond for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, certainly. Wait... What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a butler, you should \Ndodge easy attacks like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't protect your mistress \Nif you're that feeble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! W-Wait a moment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You got some problem with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was told to show our visitor \Nto the drawing room, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so you're not gonna get mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after I pushed you around like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir, so this is where you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares where the heck I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Young Sir"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Young Sir, \NI have a bit of a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? If it's about this guy, \NI don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that is not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is \Nthat machine behind you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.92,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Security 8801
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?! It's floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has a Minovsky drive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:20:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beep! Target sighted! \NImmediately moving to eliminate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate! Eliminate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know! That is why I asked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd know anything about \Nsome stupid Sanzenin mecha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beep!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gack! More from the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:19.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... I don't know what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:21.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but as a Sanzenin family butler,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to safely escort our visitors \Nto the drawing room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Sanzenin butler, the one thing \NI will ensure is safety for our guests...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that! Don't hold me \Nagainst your sopping wet clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-To handle a girl's body so familiarly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's depraved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see, pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't do this! \NIf you struggle like that in the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I certainly did ask you \Nto show them to the drawing room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to bring them \Nin through the ceiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My apologies...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, that's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will I do if I become \Nruined for marriage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who in the world are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This boy is Wataru Tachibana
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.39,0:21:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he is Nagi's... betrothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:29.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru, a mysterious boy, who has come \Nto see Nagi, and his maid, Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:30.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And Isumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:33.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Wataru really betrothed to Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:35.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With signs of even more troubling \Ntimes in the next episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:37.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,he will battle the vast \Nsubterranean labyrinth of Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:39.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:43.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hmm... Hold on a sec, \Nthere was one more person here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:51.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:57.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Moshi boku no yume ga kimi no kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:57.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If my dreams have taken your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:02.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kizutsuke-tetara
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:02.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And brought it pain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:08.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sono omoi wa itsuka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:08.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, that anguish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:11.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Boku ga morau yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:11.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take from you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:17.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Taisetsu na mono ni furue-nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:17.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While trembling over something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:23.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kakezuri-mawatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:23.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And madly dashing about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:29.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seou itami ni hibi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:29.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The hurt I bore made the days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:33.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Muimi ni sugita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:33.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Go by emptily
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:39.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oikaketa mama de oikosare-tsuzuke
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:39.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just chasing and continually being overtaken
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:44.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tohou ni kureru kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:44.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A wind who's lost its bearing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:49.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi no doko ni furetara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:49.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of you should I touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:55.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ii ka o sagashita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:55.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I sought it out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:23:00.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mamoritai yo kimi dake wa tsuyoku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:23:00.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You alone, I want to protect so much
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:05.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yokubou no wadachi kara touzakatte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:05.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting away from the rut of desire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.03,0:23:10.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Itsuka subete te ni ireru sore ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.03,0:23:10.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, it will all be ours and that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:14.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi to boku no Proof
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:14.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is our proof, yours and mine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.03,0:23:25.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Namida mo zenbu azukeru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.03,0:23:25.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Even all my tears, I entrust to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:29.47,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sign: Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.03,0:23:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nagi Sanzenin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've just started this segment today, \Nbut what exactly is this segment for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this segment, we'll follow your \Nprogress as you become a fine butler
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.99,0:23:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take a stand against a gigantic evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.07,0:23:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gigantic evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what's this song \Nplaying in the background?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes, this is my image song, \Ncomposed by the famous maestro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It perfectly conveys my \Ndesire to protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is that right? \NI'll be counting on you, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.70,0:23:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:59.33,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:24:00.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Nagi's new butler, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.33,0:24:19.31,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.16,0:24:02.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes, my name is Hayate Ayasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.42,0:24:06.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're here anyway, \Nhow about a little duel before breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.38,0:24:10.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is it the norm for the rich and \Nfamous to have duels in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.20,0:24:13.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but he probably \Nwants to show off how cool he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.25,0:24:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just beat the crap out of him for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.69,0:24:17.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.22,0:24:18.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Man's Fight".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:24:20.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to meet your fate, you stupid butler?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Man's Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.89,0:24:22.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.35,0:24:24.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots more fan service coming next time!
